verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
I am not mine own,
I've been bought with a price.
Precious blood of Christ,
I am not mine own.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
I belong to You,
I've been bought with a price.
Precious blood of Christ,
I belong to You.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
How could I ever say,
"I will choose another way",
Knowing the price that's paid;
Precious blood of Christ.
